    <p class="text-gray-black dark:text-text-white mt-10 text-base max-w-md"><span class="text-orange-semi-black dark:text-orange-semi-white/80">Computer science student and web developer</span>, specialized in creating <span class="text-main-color dark:text-main-color/80">robust web solutions.</span> Driven by a passion for technology, I’m dedicated to delivering <span class="text-main-color dark:text-main-color/80">creative, efficient, and impactful</span> solutions that transform <span class="text-orange-semi-black dark:text-orange-semi-white/80">ideas into reality</span>.</p>
